/**
 * @defgroup MIDILAR_Examples Example Programs
 * @brief Illustrative usage patterns and reference implementations for the MIDILAR framework.
 *
 * This group provides a curated set of examples demonstrating how to use MIDILAR components
 * in real-world scenarios. Each example focuses on showcasing recommended usage patterns,
 * integration strategies, and modular design principles within the context of DSP and MIDI control.
 * 
 * Examples range from waveform generation and shaping to dynamic modulation and real-time MIDI mapping.
 * They serve as both tutorials and functional test cases for embedded and desktop workflows.
 *
 * See also: `Examples.dox` for detailed summaries and links.
 */
